@host = https://localhost:7191

### 1. Ollama status
GET {{host}}/api/system/ollama

### 2. Warm local models
POST {{host}}/api/system/warmup

### 3. Seed demo data
POST {{host}}/api/demo/seed

### 4. Inspect documents
GET {{host}}/api/documents?tenantId=company-1

### 5. Inspect chunks and embedding preview/full vector
GET {{host}}/api/documents/vacation-policy-v7/chunks?tenantId=company-1&includeEmbedding=false

### 6. Retrieval only - no chat LLM
POST {{host}}/api/search/semantic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "company-1",
  "userId": "naor",
  "roles": ["employee"],
  "query": "How many vacation days can be carried into next year?",
  "topK": 10,
  "minimumSimilarity": 0.1
}

### 7. Complete RAG pipeline
POST {{host}}/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "company-1",
  "userId": "naor",
  "roles": ["employee"],
  "question": "How many vacation days can be carried into next year?",
  "evaluateGroundedness": true
}

### 8. Tenant isolation test - must not retrieve company-2's 10-day rule
POST {{host}}/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "company-1",
  "userId": "naor",
  "roles": ["employee"],
  "question": "Can employees carry over 10 vacation days?",
  "evaluateGroundedness": false
}

### 9. Role authorization test - employee must not retrieve HR policy
POST {{host}}/api/search/semantic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "company-1",
  "userId": "naor",
  "roles": ["employee"],
  "query": "When is the annual salary review?"
}

### 10. Same query as HR
POST {{host}}/api/search/semantic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "company-1",
  "userId": "hr-user",
  "roles": ["hr"],
  "query": "When is the annual salary review?"
}

### Recent traces
GET {{host}}/api/traces?count=20

### 11. Inspect one embedding
POST {{host}}/api/debug/embedding
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Remaining annual leave can be carried into the following year.",
  "purpose": "Query",
  "includeFullVector": false
}

### 12. Compare semantic similarity
POST {{host}}/api/debug/similarity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "textA": "Employees may transfer unused vacation days.",
  "textB": "Remaining annual leave can be carried into the following year.",
  "purposeA": "Query",
  "purposeB": "Document"
}

### 13. Call the LLM directly without RAG
POST {{host}}/api/debug/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systemPrompt": "You are concise.",
  "userPrompt": "Explain embeddings in one sentence.",
  "temperature": 0
}
